          "plain_text": "We’re off to the Tate Modern; a museum that I’ve heard so much about. On the walk we find a box of things on the street - I come away with a bag scale. Something that I’ve often found myself wanting. Finding free things on the street that people are throwing out is truly such a special gem in London. ",
          "href": null
        }
      ],
