    "paragraph": {
      "rich_text": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": {
            "content": "We take a bus and manage to get the front row seats on the top deck. As always I’m immersed in watching the beautiful streets, buildings, people and parks blur by. The bus takes us to the Millennium Bridge where we cross the Thames to get to the Tate. Georgie had told us to watch out for painted pieces of bubble gum in the bridge but we don’t spot them. ",
            "link": null
          },
