          "plain_text": "We head over to Marks & Spencer to do some grocery shopping. It’s basically Woolworths in London - we even find one hand wash with almonds that has exactly the same label and bottle as the equivalent product back in South Africa. We struggle a little bit with the automated checkout machine but Michael the assistant realises that we are suffering and lends many a hand. ",
